â€¢ Hearsay & Personal Knowledge ğŸ‘‚ â€” Stick to what you saw, did, or received. Quote short portions and attach the document. Identify who said what, when, and how you know.
â€¢ Use Cases ğŸ¯ â€” Support TRO/PI, summary judgment, motions to compel, objections, sanctions, and to create an appeal-proof factual record when hearings are limited or not recorded.
